Sh. Rahul Sharma
(AR) is present on behalf of the promoter. 

Sh. Mohinder Singh, Sh. Jasbeer Singh, Sh. Chanderbhan Singh, Sh.
Satyawan, Sh. Narender Pal, Sh. Satpal and Sh. Bijender, landowners are present
before the authority and states that they have no concern/objection with regard
